000100 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
000200 PROGRAM-ID. EVALUATECOMPLEX.
000300*
000400 DATA DIVISION.
000500 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
000600 01  WS-GRADE         PIC 9(3) VALUE ZEROS.
000700 01  WS-MSG           PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
000800*
000900 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
001000 MAIN-PARA.
001100*    Test EVALUATE with multiple WHEN clauses
001200     MOVE 95 TO WS-GRADE.
001300     PERFORM CHECK-GRADE.
001400     MOVE 75 TO WS-GRADE.
001500     PERFORM CHECK-GRADE.
001600     MOVE 50 TO WS-GRADE.
001700     PERFORM CHECK-GRADE.
001800     MOVE 30 TO WS-GRADE.
001900     PERFORM CHECK-GRADE.
