002100     MOVE 100 TO WS-GRADE.
002200     IF WS-GRADE > 90
002300         DISPLAY "HONOR ROLL"
002400     ELSE
002500         IF WS-GRADE > 70
002600             DISPLAY "PASSING"
002700         ELSE
002800             DISPLAY "NEEDS WORK"
002900         END-IF
003000     END-IF.
003100     STOP RUN.
003200*
003300 CHECK-GRADE.
003400     EVALUATE WS-GRADE
003500         WHEN 95
003600             DISPLAY "A"
003700         WHEN 75
003800             DISPLAY "C"
003900         WHEN 50
004000             DISPLAY "F"
004100         WHEN OTHER
004200             DISPLAY "UNKNOWN"
004300     END-EVALUATE.
